- Ming'an is outside.
- Anran.

44
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,360
Let go of me first.

45
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,320
Anran.

46
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,640
What happened?

47
