60
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,760
The Helian Zheng you despise

61
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,040
wouldn't even let a rose's thorn

62
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,440
prick you.

63
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,880
But you don't love him.

64
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,600
Between him and me...

65
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,720
Tell me,

66
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,520
is my bullet faster,

67
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:55,400
or him calling for help faster?

68
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,040
Anran, what's wrong?

69
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,280
What happened?

70
