98
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,760
Please keep it
for someone who truly loves you.

99
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,200
But you and He Zheng are impossible.

100
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,280
You're siblings.

101
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,960
You are the He Family's heiress,

102
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,640
and he remains the stepson.

103
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,520
There's no other choice

104
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,480
for you two.

105
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:55,520
♪Silent sentiments, shattered colors♪

106
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:58,600
