109
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,050
There's no logic to it.

110
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:06,200
♪Can't break free♪

111
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:08,360
Even if he can only be my brother,

112
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,600
I have the memories

113
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,440
of our time together to cherish.

114
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,280
That's enough.

115
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,860
